imary__list"><li class="nav-primary__item nav-primary__item--first"><a href="#mainMenu">Menu</a></li><li class="nav-primary__item"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/">Home</a></li><li class="nav-primary__item"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/browse">Browse</a></li><li class="nav-primary__item"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/magazine">Magazine</a></li><li class="nav-primary__item"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/community">Community</a></li><li class="nav-primary__item"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/about">About</a></li></ul></nav><nav class="nav-secondary"><ul class="nav-secondary__list"><li class="nav-secondary__item nav-secondary__item--search"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/search" rel="search">Search</a></li><li class="nav-secondary__item nav-secondary__item--alert"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/content-alerts">Alerts</a></li><li class="nav-secondary__item"><a href="https://elifesciences.org/submit-your-research" class="block-button block-button__variant-one">Submit your research</a></li></ul></nav></div></div></div><div class="primary-section-header"><header class="content-header"><ul class="article-flag-list"><li class="article-flag-list__item"><a class="article-flag__link" href="https://elifesciences.org/subjects/genetics-genomics">Genetics and Genomics</a></li><li class="article-flag-list__item"><a class="article-flag__link" href="https://elifesciences.org/subjects/medicine">Medicine</a></li></ul><h1 class="title">Allelic strengths of encephalopathy-associated <em>UBA5</em> variants correlate between <em>in vivo</em> and <em>in vitro</em> assays</h1><div class="
